00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:57,640
the internal network one leg is connected to the DMZ and the other leg is connected to the outside

76
00:08:57,640 --> 00:09:05,640
internet but there's nothing stopping companies from having four legs or five legs or a hundred

77
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:12,600
legs or legs within other legs so the bottom line is companies can get pretty creative in how they

78
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:19,320
structure how they they first of all put their firewalls in here and how they offer functionality

79
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:25,160
related to services that may be required so you can get pretty creative not only in the functionality

